{"tid":750830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰英國飛港班機故障無零件　乘客苦等27個鐘","createTime":"2018-07-21T10:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T10:29:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63312782b57ab06ff3879583f39510c7c823c9b6","tid":750830,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名跌至第六的國泰航空</span></span></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一班由英國曼徹斯特飛香港的航機嚴重延誤27小時！涉事的航班原定今早(21日)6時55分到達香港，惟國泰向乘客發出通知，指因技術問題，航機需延遲逾27小時起飛，暫料明日(22日)上午10時才能到達香港。有乘客鬧爆國泰敷衍，不盡力安排繼續旅程，致旅客行程受阻。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名受影響乘客向東網投訴，指收到國泰一張通知，稱航班CX216因技術故障需要維修，其中有替換零件需由香港運到曼徹斯特，故造成今次嚴重延誤。通知又指由於昨日(20日)是英國學校放假後的第一個周末，難以安排乘客轉乘其他航班，故唯一選項是讓多數乘客等候航班維修。<br />\n<br />\n該通知又提到，已安排酒店讓受影響乘客入住，向所有受影響乘客致歉。東網正向國泰了解事件，暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180721/bkn-20180721154735853-0721_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180721%2Fbkn-20180721154735853-0721_00822_001.html&d=%2FGrfE0Fn325czZ%2FxUEZaLdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0ca63c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180721/bkn-20180721154735853-0721_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4843a486b4babdcf01743466b1e0a214d7abb39f","tid":750830,"uid":33439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"入黎為咗睇第一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bbfc67d99b2306161771c12d178301f4b74941","tid":750830,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"compensation claim 到fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d32e76e3c9c94448